      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what do you mean \"the game\"? i'm not talking about a video game. i'm talking about the actual sky outside on the train. i was looking out the window at the real world and it looked like a broken asset. i know how it sounds but i felt like i was seeing through the simulation for a second. don't you think the idea that we're in a simulation is actually a plausible theory?",
